title: MID/ADC Looking for a team.
body: Hey guys, I'm in b5 but I genuinely feel that I don't belong there. I'm looking for a team to play with cause I've pretty much given up on soloq after the changes to the prelims. I don't mind having to try out or go through an initiation since I'm in b5. Give me a chance bruhs

replies.body: You might want to give more information about what you are looking for and your experience and your goals, preferred role and best champs etc.
